nodes.text: Kthira'shi'ktarloo, better known by his core name, Ashik, was a male Chiss who served as the head of personal security and an aide to Imperial Head of State Jagged Fel. After a kidnap attempt on Fel, Ashik, along with a number of Imperial Security guards, was the first to arrive at Fel's embassy quarters. He later assisted Fel in a space battle against Imperial defectors in 44 ABY.
